CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 27, 1945, pg. 15, reads: "Sequoias - These young ladies are tossing a hop at the Parish House, Centre Avenue, on November 2.  Left to right: Frances Parr, Yvonne Hall, Betty Hord, Alma Rector, Emogene [Imogene] Parrin [Perrin], Virginia Jackson and Maxine Wright. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Sequoias club members, squatting from left: Betty Hord (Jones), Alma Rector, Imogene Perrin; standing: Yvonne Hall, Frances Parr, Virginia Jackson, and Maxine Wright posed in front of Pittsburgh Courier newspaper billboard with image of soldier on stretcher
